reviewText: I absolutely love this movie! Hope it comes on dvd one day!

I first saw this movie when I was a teenager.  Story takes place in an orphanage(all boy) where a brother and a sister live.  She loves to play soccer and wants to live in the orphanage.  Only problem, boys only.  So, she dresses up as a boy and plays soccer and lives there.  No one discovers that she is a girl for the longest time.  She is accepted for who she is.  Watch it to find out how it ends.
